item.title: Are You Sure You Don't Need to Use the Toilet
item.description: Daddies ask their daughters to be sure they've gone to the bathroom before setting off on a long drive. Sometimes daddies know best. But daughters ask their daddies too. Annie's daddy makes a second kind of pee, and she knows he has to do it in the very special toilet that she has tucked up between her legs. Sometimes daughters know best.
